          ### A monthly newsletter on mobile design

          A well-designed SaaS is crucial for improving customer retention and reducing churn. You understand this and value great design, but getting started can feel daunting. All you want is to learn how to make real progress from a professional. That’s why I focus on sending you actionable articles on mobile design every month.

          From customer onboarding and app notifications, to mobile design best practices, you’ll get in-depth articles that’ll wow your customers. My goal is to make it as easy as possible for you to start making significant changes to your business.

          Grid North Design is a solo business run by Richard Child (that’s me!), a mobile designer who’s worked in the travel industry for over 3 years. Previous clients include: Cabify, GNARBOX, Accent, JensonR+ and Nusii. Sign up now to get in-depth guides, articles, and downloadable resources on mobile design for travel startups.

